**Section 3**: FAQ — 5 questions [Manual §3, §4, §11, §13]:

1. **How is CMR DMS deployed?** — The platform is deployed on your server infrastructure. There is no shared multi-tenant cloud. Your documents, your server, your control.
2. **How long does onboarding take?** — Most organizations are operational within a few days. Initial setup involves configuring categories, adding users and roles, setting your storage backend, and uploading your company branding.
3. **Can we white-label the platform?** — Yes. Upload your logo and banner, and set your company name as the browser title. Every user sees your branding from the login screen onward.
4. **Is multi-language support available?** — Yes. Administrators can add, update, and remove language options. The full interface is available in any configured language.
5. **Does it integrate with our existing email infrastructure?** — Yes. Configure any SMTP server (or multiple, with a default) to handle all outgoing notifications, reminders, and document-sharing emails.

