## SHARED COMPONENT SPECS

### Scroll Animations (`js/animations.js`)

Use the **Intersection Observer API** — no GSAP required (use GSAP if you choose to, via CDN).

- Elements with class `.reveal` fade in from `opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px)` when they enter the viewport. Stagger children with `.reveal-children > *` applying increasing `transition-delay` (0ms, 80ms, 160ms, 240ms...).
- Stat counters: When a `.stat-counter` element enters the viewport, animate the number from 0 to its `data-target` value over 1.8 seconds with easeOutExpo easing.
- Timeline items on `how-it-works.html`: slide in from left or right alternately.
- FAQ accordion items: smooth `max-height` transition for expand/collapse. Only one item open at a time.

### Button Styles

```css
/* Solid accent */
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 10px, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background: #00F5DA;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 201, 177, 0.4);
}

/* Ghost */
.btn-ghost {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  /* same sizing and font as btn-primary */
}
.btn-ghost:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  color: var(--accent);
}
```

### Cards

```css
.card {
  background: var(--bg-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 32px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
}
.card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(0, 201, 177, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0, 201, 177, 0.07);
}
```

No border-radius on cards or buttons. The chamfered corner on primary buttons and sharp rectangular cards reinforce the precision aesthetic.

### Section Layout

```css
section {
  padding: 120px clamp(20px, 6vw, 120px);
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.eyebrow {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
h2 {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
```

